      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. so if the light part is all about splitting water and getting electrons, what's the deal with the Calvin cycle? i don't quite get how it actually uses the ATP and NADPH to make stuff out of CO2. can u walk me through the steps of that part specifically?",
      "source": "evaluator"
